WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:09.320 --> 00:01:10.640
Write down everything I just said.

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:10.970
Okay.

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:11.960
Ah.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:13.000
Make it detailed.

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:19.280
Wait a minute, I need to take a call.

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:20.210
Hello, go ahead.

00:01:20.360 --> 00:01:23.840
Master, people familiar with Wang Xichuan and his son revealed they had a bad relationship.

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:25.770
They often argued and even fought.

00:01:26.280 --> 00:01:27.080
A couple of days ago,

00:01:27.080 --> 00:01:28.200
Wang Mingming even threatened him with a knife,

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:30.130
saying he would kill Wang Xichuan.

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:32.320
This person is a major suspect.

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:33.200
Where is he now?

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:34.280
The villagers said

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:37.539
they haven't seen Wang Mingming go out these past two days.

00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:38.160
That means

00:01:38.720 --> 00:01:40.450
he's most likely still at home.

00:01:41.160 --> 00:01:42.600
Call Qiu Chen right now.

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:43.479
Keep calling until you get through.

00:01:43.479 --> 00:01:43.960
Understand?

00:01:43.960 --> 00:01:44.690
Understood.

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:00.320
Hello, Zhai.

00:02:00.320 --> 00:02:01.050
Hello, Chen.

00:02:01.600 --> 00:02:02.200
Did you...

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:04.800
Did you ask...

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:08.199
Wang Xichuan's son, Wang Mingming,

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:11.020
might still be at home.

00:02:11.840 --> 00:02:12.160
Who?

00:02:28.160 --> 00:02:28.600
Sir.

00:02:29.200 --> 00:02:30.000
Handcuff him.

00:02:30.800 --> 00:02:31.960
Sir, you're injured.

00:02:31.960 --> 00:02:32.560
What injury?

00:02:32.560 --> 00:02:33.040
Handcuff him.

00:02:33.040 --> 00:02:33.480
Okay.

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:36.000
You even dare to slash a cop.

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:37.600
Assaulting an officer, huh?

00:02:37.720 --> 00:02:39.840
I thought it was a thief.

00:02:51.640 --> 00:02:52.280
Dad.

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:53.320
Dad.

00:02:54.240 --> 00:02:54.770
Qiu Chen.

00:02:55.960 --> 00:02:57.090
Qiu Chen, calm down.

00:02:59.360 --> 00:02:59.640
Dad.

00:03:00.520 --> 00:03:00.920
Dad.

00:03:01.640 --> 00:03:02.240
Calm down.

00:03:07.640 --> 00:03:08.240
Gu Yuming.

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:27.000
Yes.

00:03:27.600 --> 00:03:28.860
Why are you still here?

00:03:29.480 --> 00:03:30.480
It's almost dawn.

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:32.140
I'm not sleepy.

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:34.200
Did you find the head?

00:03:35.160 --> 00:03:35.840
Not yet.

00:03:36.160 --> 00:03:36.800
Go back and get some rest.

00:03:36.800 --> 00:03:37.200
Hey.

00:03:38.320 --> 00:03:38.960
How about

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:41.440
you go back and rest for a few days.

00:03:41.440 --> 00:03:42.640
I will find that head.

00:03:44.960 --> 00:03:45.520
Qiu Chen.

00:03:46.640 --> 00:03:47.440
I understand you.

00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:49.640
You have your own way of investigating.

00:03:49.800 --> 00:03:51.720
And you're eager to solve the case.

00:03:51.720 --> 00:03:52.320
But I ask you

00:03:52.320 --> 00:03:54.400
not to act alone on missions anymore.

00:03:56.240 --> 00:03:56.680
Also,

00:03:57.440 --> 00:03:59.360
don't wear this piece of junk anymore.

00:03:59.360 --> 00:04:01.020
It was so dangerous this time.

00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:04.240
I wasn't listening to the earphones when I was handling the case.

00:04:04.240 --> 00:04:05.960
Besides, my dad gave me these.

00:04:07.880 --> 00:04:09.160
When to wear them and when not to,

00:04:09.160 --> 00:04:10.360
I know what I'm doing.

00:04:11.640 --> 00:04:13.040
Your dad gave them to you?

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:14.360
Let me see.

00:04:17.640 --> 00:04:18.240
All right,

00:04:18.320 --> 00:04:19.980
hurry back and get some sleep.

00:04:23.080 --> 00:04:24.960
[coughs]

00:04:27.760 --> 00:04:28.560
Ouch.

00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:33.409
A butcher knife,

00:04:34.920 --> 00:04:36.120
and these body parts.

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:38.560
The evidence is conclusive.

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:40.650
What else do you have to say?

00:04:45.720 --> 00:04:46.880
This butcher knife

00:04:47.159 --> 00:04:49.560
is the weapon you used to kill Wang Xichuan.

00:04:49.560 --> 00:04:51.420
Only your fingerprints are on it.

00:04:52.920 --> 00:04:54.480
I didn't kill anyone.

00:04:55.280 --> 00:04:55.400
No,

00:04:55.400 --> 00:04:57.640
I was still counting on that old bastard to buy me drinks.

00:04:57.640 --> 00:04:58.770
Why would I kill him?

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:02.140
Where did you go the night before yesterday,

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:03.220
and what did you do?

00:05:06.440 --> 00:05:07.280
Ouch.

00:05:09.560 --> 00:05:10.520
Ah.

00:05:12.280 --> 00:05:13.080
That night...

00:05:14.960 --> 00:05:16.480
I was drunk.

00:05:16.480 --> 00:05:17.560
I was drunk.

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:19.760
I...

00:05:20.480 --> 00:05:22.080
No, officer.

00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:25.360
Can you get me some wine?

00:05:25.360 --> 00:05:27.160
I can't take it. I feel terrible.

00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:30.880
Dad, give me some wine.

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:33.000
Dad, where are you?

00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:34.840
Behave yourself.

00:05:42.280 --> 00:05:42.880
Oh.

00:05:44.440 --> 00:05:45.400
I remember now.

00:05:47.480 --> 00:05:48.600
I...

00:05:49.640 --> 00:05:50.480
I did

00:05:50.720 --> 00:05:53.080
argue with that old bastard.

00:06:11.920 --> 00:06:12.720
Wang Xichuan!

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:14.600
Give me money.

00:06:15.080 --> 00:06:15.400
Tsk.

00:06:16.640 --> 00:06:17.840
Money.

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:19.600
All day long,

00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:21.920
you only know to ask me for money.

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:24.460
I don't have money either.

00:06:26.560 --> 00:06:27.920
Dad.

00:06:28.920 --> 00:06:31.920
I haven't had money for wine recently.

00:06:31.920 --> 00:06:33.760
I saw everything today.

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:35.000
That woman

00:06:35.800 --> 00:06:37.400
asked you to change her luck.

00:06:37.560 --> 00:06:38.880
You made a lot, right?

00:06:41.520 --> 00:06:44.080
Earn it yourself.

00:06:46.880 --> 00:06:47.600
How?

00:06:48.720 --> 00:06:49.760
Like you,

00:06:50.760 --> 00:06:52.200
by swindling and bluffing?

00:06:52.200 --> 00:06:53.760
Hahaha.

00:06:56.760 --> 00:06:58.280
You are a grown man,

00:06:58.760 --> 00:06:59.960
with hands and feet.

00:07:01.080 --> 00:07:03.810
But you don't even have the ability to earn money.

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:05.040
You

00:07:06.480 --> 00:07:07.800
are just a loser.

00:07:10.520 --> 00:07:11.320
Wang Xichuan!

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:13.730
I'm telling you.

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:16.360
I'm your only son.

00:07:17.040 --> 00:07:18.500
If you don't give me money,

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:20.220
I'll die right in front of you.

00:07:20.400 --> 00:07:21.160
Hehe.

00:07:21.800 --> 00:07:23.000
I'd like to see

00:07:23.320 --> 00:07:24.280
how you die.

00:07:25.240 --> 00:07:26.100
Hang yourself,

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:28.740
commit suicide, or slit your wrists.

00:07:28.920 --> 00:07:29.600
Show me.

00:07:34.640 --> 00:07:36.120
Hehe.

00:07:36.480 --> 00:07:42.480
Hahaha.

00:07:42.480 --> 00:07:43.560
You give me...

00:07:51.440 --> 00:07:53.880
I didn't hack him with a knife.

00:07:53.960 --> 00:07:55.040
He is my dad.

00:07:55.040 --> 00:07:57.360
How could a son hack his own father?

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:59.159
So you still know he's your father.

00:07:59.159 --> 00:07:59.760
No.

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:01.520
You beat your own father,

00:08:01.520 --> 00:08:02.850
and slashed the police.

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:04.960
Is there anything you wouldn't dare do?

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:06.080
Give me a sip of liquor,

00:08:06.080 --> 00:08:08.280
and I'll tell you everything.

00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:09.200
I beg you.

00:08:10.280 --> 00:08:11.720
Dad, where are you?

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:13.360
I want a drink.

00:08:13.360 --> 00:08:14.240
Dad!

00:08:14.320 --> 00:08:15.320
Wang Xichuan,

00:08:15.600 --> 00:08:16.440
where are you?

00:08:16.640 --> 00:08:17.360
Dad!

00:08:17.560 --> 00:08:19.480
I miss you. I want to drink.

00:08:19.600 --> 00:08:21.260
When attacking me last night,

00:08:21.520 --> 00:08:23.240
their movements were noticeably uncoordinated.

00:08:23.240 --> 00:08:26.640
With weak wrists, it'd be hard to do the dismemberment alone.

00:08:33.240 --> 00:08:33.570
Sigh.

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:36.370
Wang Mingming must have drunk fake booze.

00:08:36.600 --> 00:08:37.240
Xiao Zhai,

00:08:37.960 --> 00:08:39.000
get me a Coke.

00:08:39.320 --> 00:08:39.919
Master.

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:42.919
No sugar-free Coke today.

00:08:43.600 --> 00:08:45.200
Let's have something sweet.

00:08:45.320 --> 00:08:45.520
Ah.

00:08:45.960 --> 00:08:46.240
Hey.

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:47.560
This case

00:08:48.320 --> 00:08:49.120
is too bitter.

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:51.050
Sigh.

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:51.560
Mhm.

00:08:52.160 --> 00:08:52.620
Thanks.

00:08:56.280 --> 00:08:56.440
Here.

00:08:56.440 --> 00:08:56.920
Oh.

00:08:56.920 --> 00:08:58.520
I knew you wouldn't drink it.

00:08:58.520 --> 00:08:59.720
I bought you two cups.

00:09:00.040 --> 00:09:02.100
Jasmine green milk tea and taro boba.

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:03.280
They are your favorites.

00:09:03.280 --> 00:09:04.280
Get out of the way.

00:09:04.640 --> 00:09:06.280
Hey, this milk tea is good. Where did you buy it?

00:09:06.280 --> 00:09:07.280
Just downstairs.

00:09:07.600 --> 00:09:08.440
I bought these four cups.

00:09:08.440 --> 00:09:10.240
Are we still having the meeting?

00:09:14.880 --> 00:09:15.880
Ah, stop drinking.

00:09:15.880 --> 00:09:17.040
Come on, be serious.

00:09:17.680 --> 00:09:19.720
The disciplinary committee member is speaking.

00:09:19.720 --> 00:09:20.120
Mm.

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:20.850
Let's start.

00:09:25.160 --> 00:09:26.720
For people like Wang Mingming,

00:09:26.720 --> 00:09:28.320
who are chronic alcoholics,

00:09:28.800 --> 00:09:30.930
they are prone to chronic alcoholism,

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:33.200
leading to alcoholic cerebellar degeneration.

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:34.330
The typical symptom

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:35.560
is ataxia.

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:38.680
If it's severe,

00:09:39.280 --> 00:09:40.920
even dismemberment,

00:09:41.400 --> 00:09:45.130
a delicate operation requiring high coordination and stability,

00:09:45.280 --> 00:09:47.080
would be very difficult for him.

00:09:47.120 --> 00:09:48.040
Or rather,

00:09:48.360 --> 00:09:49.320
impossible.

00:09:50.120 --> 00:09:52.780
Because he probably couldn't even hold a knife.

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:55.080
Yeah, Captain Gu.

00:09:55.400 --> 00:09:57.880
According to Wang Mingming's blood test,

00:09:57.920 --> 00:10:00.380
he suffers from severe chronic alcoholism,

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:03.640
which has already caused alcoholic cerebellar degeneration.

00:10:03.640 --> 00:10:05.040
Based on our evaluation,

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:07.680
he couldn't possibly have dismembered the body alone.

00:10:07.680 --> 00:10:08.010
Yeah.

00:10:08.680 --> 00:10:09.610
I checked again.

00:10:09.920 --> 00:10:12.440
Although Wang Mingming worked in a slaughterhouse before,

00:10:12.440 --> 00:10:14.100
he was just an employee in name

00:10:14.120 --> 00:10:15.450
and barely went to work.

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:18.800
So,

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:20.200
it wasn't Wang Mingming.

00:10:22.160 --> 00:10:25.020
At least he wasn't the one who dismembered the body.

00:10:25.480 --> 00:10:27.240
He either had an accomplice,

00:10:27.440 --> 00:10:28.240
or

00:10:28.640 --> 00:10:30.440
the real killer is someone else.

00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:32.160
Then how do we explain

00:10:32.680 --> 00:10:34.140
the evidence at the scene?

00:10:35.040 --> 00:10:37.040
That's exactly what I wanted to say.

00:10:37.800 --> 00:10:39.960
The scene was disguised too perfectly.

00:10:39.960 --> 00:10:41.080
All the evidence

00:10:41.720 --> 00:10:42.780
points to a suspect

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:44.220
with plenty of motives

00:10:44.840 --> 00:10:46.080
but no capability.

00:10:49.280 --> 00:10:51.140
Don't you think it's suspicious?

00:10:54.720 --> 00:10:56.520
He is not the real killer.

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:00.320
Then who could the killer be?

00:11:03.920 --> 00:11:05.850
When Wang Mingming was taken away,

00:11:06.360 --> 00:11:07.920
he glanced at the kitchen.

00:11:08.600 --> 00:11:10.440
Maybe there is something hidden there

00:11:10.440 --> 00:11:12.360
that he is afraid of being found.

00:11:21.360 --> 00:11:23.220
What exactly are you looking for?

00:12:04.920 --> 00:12:06.160
This scratch.

00:12:13.480 --> 00:12:13.940
Come on.

00:12:15.480 --> 00:12:16.010
One, two.

00:12:16.960 --> 00:12:17.640
Wow.

00:12:19.600 --> 00:12:20.660
What's that smell?

00:12:23.200 --> 00:12:23.840
Woah.

00:12:35.120 --> 00:12:35.840
Siyu said,

00:12:36.280 --> 00:12:38.160
the two female skeletons found in the crop field

00:12:38.160 --> 00:12:40.640
have been matched through the missing persons DNA database.

00:12:40.640 --> 00:12:44.570
They are confirmed to be the two girls who went missing three years ago.

00:12:44.880 --> 00:12:45.800
OK, I got it.

00:12:52.240 --> 00:12:52.970
Who's there?

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:53.880
Be careful.

00:12:58.560 --> 00:12:59.320
Who are you?

00:13:00.640 --> 00:13:01.440
Answer me.

00:13:02.600 --> 00:13:03.520
Speak.

00:13:04.000 --> 00:13:05.000
What's your name?

00:13:09.120 --> 00:13:10.780
She seems mentally unstable.

00:13:15.560 --> 00:13:16.440
She's chained.

00:13:19.080 --> 00:13:19.640
Siyu.

00:13:20.720 --> 00:13:22.000
We are at Wang Xichuan's,

00:13:22.000 --> 00:13:22.920
down in their cellar,

00:13:22.920 --> 00:13:24.520
and we found a captive woman.

00:13:25.520 --> 00:13:26.980
And she's a bit delirious.

00:13:28.360 --> 00:13:30.020
Bring your team over here now.

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:30.640
Yes.

00:13:30.880 --> 00:13:32.340
Yeah, as soon as possible.

00:13:37.240 --> 00:13:38.720
Who locked you up here?

00:13:39.960 --> 00:13:40.960
Do you know?

00:13:43.760 --> 00:13:44.760
By the looks of it,

00:13:44.800 --> 00:13:46.800
she's been locked up for a long time.

00:13:50.440 --> 00:13:51.370
Look at the wall.

00:14:01.200 --> 00:14:02.200
It's Nüshu again.

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:10.930
You're all here.

00:14:11.040 --> 00:14:11.700
Captain Gu.

00:14:11.840 --> 00:14:12.570
Listen to me.

00:14:12.840 --> 00:14:13.680
Inside and outside the house,

00:14:13.680 --> 00:14:15.040
every room and every corner,

00:14:15.040 --> 00:14:16.440
search them thoroughly.

00:14:16.520 --> 00:14:17.720
Do not miss any details.

00:14:17.720 --> 00:14:18.440
Understood?

00:14:18.440 --> 00:14:19.000
Understood.

00:14:19.000 --> 00:14:19.320
Go.

00:14:29.880 --> 00:14:30.560
Zhai.

00:14:30.600 --> 00:14:31.080
Yes.

00:14:57.880 --> 00:15:00.540
It seems this is the actual dismemberment site.

00:15:18.520 --> 00:15:19.240
Tweezers.

00:15:22.600 --> 00:15:23.660
Mai, evidence bag.

00:15:58.120 --> 00:15:58.780
Captain Gu,

00:15:58.880 --> 00:16:00.080
there are heads here.

00:16:00.320 --> 00:16:01.980
We found Wang Xichuan's head.

00:16:04.920 --> 00:16:06.320
Based on the size,

00:16:07.920 --> 00:16:09.580
they look like women's heads.

00:16:11.200 --> 00:16:12.080
It's possible.

00:16:12.680 --> 00:16:14.320
These should be from the tall crop field,

00:16:14.320 --> 00:16:16.980
the heads of those two headless female corpses.

00:16:26.520 --> 00:16:28.040
If that's the case,

00:16:29.560 --> 00:16:30.840
Wang Xichuan's head

00:16:31.280 --> 00:16:33.210
must have been placed here before.

00:16:34.320 --> 00:16:36.720
He also witnessed his own dismemberment.

00:16:47.000 --> 00:16:47.760
Yang Xiaomei,

00:16:47.760 --> 00:16:48.690
don't be afraid.

00:16:49.520 --> 00:16:51.650
We're going to ask you a few questions.

00:16:52.040 --> 00:16:54.570
Do you remember how you got to Wangwu Village?

00:16:54.720 --> 00:16:55.650
Wangwu Village?

00:16:56.400 --> 00:16:57.600
This is... this is...

00:16:58.000 --> 00:16:58.760
Where is this?

00:16:58.760 --> 00:16:59.680
Wangwu Village?

00:16:59.680 --> 00:17:00.880
This is a hospital.

00:17:00.880 --> 00:17:02.080
You are very safe now.

00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:03.210
Before this,

00:17:03.400 --> 00:17:04.720
do you remember if you were

00:17:04.720 --> 00:17:06.040
locked in a cellar?

00:17:08.839 --> 00:17:09.400
Cellar?

00:17:10.319 --> 00:17:10.520
Cellar.

00:17:10.520 --> 00:17:11.760
Yes, in a cellar.

00:17:14.440 --> 00:17:15.760
What did you see in the cellar?

00:17:15.760 --> 00:17:16.690
Don't look at me.

00:17:19.000 --> 00:17:19.800
Don't look at me.